commit.message:
Avoid implicit function declarations in tests (#84)

Future compilers are likely to reject implicit function declarations
by default, causing these tests to fail.  Also replace () with (void)
where appropriate in the changed tests.

commit.message:
Make Makefile portable (#72)

* Make Makefile portable

- Just include Make.user directly
- Replace SunPro-style pattern rule by suffix rule; neither can merge
  targets into a single call, so no point in using $?
- Replace unportable $^ with a variable.
- Replace wildcard+sort with a call to find, also for portability.

Co-authored-by: Harmen Stoppels <harmenstoppels@gmail.com>
